<i>noun</i>: 알츠하이머 병 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>알츠하이머 병</dt><br>
<dd>a progressive form of presenile dementia that is similar to senile dementia except that it usually starts in the 40s or 50s; first symptoms are impaired memory which is followed by impaired thought and speech and finally complete helplessness</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: Alzheimer's disease, Alzheimer's, Alzheimers</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
